<DIV><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:><SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:>There has been no further update at this time regarding any of the old issues on your class list.&nbsp; I have altered the list to reflect the new items added and submitted.</SPAN></DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: level2 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .25in? 0pt list tab-stops: lfo1; l0 mso-list: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt:><SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?>1.<SPAN **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt Roman?? ?Times New>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>Increase DoT crit percentage for necros to better balance against other classes nukes<SPAN **Zowie**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:><FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN><namespace prefix = o ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI"></P>
