<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><STRONG>#2 - Lowering of DoT resists</STRONG> <FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: red?><FONT color=#66cc00><STRONG><FONT face=Verdana size=2>(Part of the proposed first pass with class re-envisioning posted on EQLive on 3/14/2005)</FONT><BR></STRONG></FONT></SPAN><BR></FONT>In order to attain adequate DPS, DoT spells must be stacked, and in a timely manner (i.e. as close to the start of a fight as possible). Resists can affect Necromancers in 2 ways: </DIV>
